---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="关于" description="王炸小纸条，注册电气工程师（发输变电），国家电网员工。用 AI 做新能源的一个人。">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>关于我</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <section class="section-block profile">
      <div class="profile-card card">
        <div class="profile-item">
          <span class="label">称呼</span>
          <span class="value">王炸小纸条</span>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-item">
          <span class="label">来自</span>
          <span class="value">江西赣州宁都</span>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-item">
          <span class="label">职业</span>
          <span class="value">国家电网 · 注册电气工程师（发输变电）</span>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-item">
          <span class="label">公众号</span>
          <span class="value">王炸小纸条</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>📍 职业轨迹</h2>
      <div class="timeline">
        <div class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-content">
            <time>毕业后</time>
            <p>中山某上市集团，写宣传报道被领导赏识。工资两千多，选择考研。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-content">
            <time>研究生毕业后</time>
            <p>进入国家电网。营销班组三年，发核心论文。后转入机关。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tl-item">
          <div class="tl-dot"></div>
          <div class="tl-content">
            <time>现在</time>
            <p>朝九晚五上班，下班研究 AI、开发工具、写公众号。马上要成为一个父亲。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>🛠️ 技能与关注</h2>
      <div class="tag-cloud">
        <span class="tag">电气工程</span>
        <span class="tag">注册电气工程师</span>
        <span class="tag">绿电直连</span>
        <span class="tag">电价改革</span>
        <span class="tag">储能配置</span>
        <span class="tag">Claude Code</span>
        <span class="tag">AI Agent</span>
        <span class="tag">Obsidian</span>
        <span class="tag">知识管理</span>
        <span class="tag">前端开发</span>
        <span class="tag">GitHub Pages</span>
        <span class="tag">Python</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>💬 座右铭</h2>
      <div class="motto-block">
        <blockquote>
          <p>但行好事，莫问前程。</p>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
          <p>按照自己喜欢的方式度过这一生。</p>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
          <p>愿你出走半生，归来仍是少年。</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block connect-section">
      <h2>📮 找到我</h2>
      <div class="connect-links">
        <a href="https://github.com/pompomdonotlike008-dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="connect-card card">
          <span class="connect-icon">🐙</span>
          <span>GitHub</span>
        </a>
        <div class="connect-card card">
          <span class="connect-icon">📱</span>
          <span>公众号：王炸小纸条</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 0 40px;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--content-padding);
  }

  .section-block {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .section-block h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .profile-card {
    padding: 24px 28px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .profile-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-placeholder);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 60px;
  }

  .value {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 24px;
    border-left: 2px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .tl-item {
    position: relative;
    padding: 16px 0 16px 20px;
  }

  .tl-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -30px;
    top: 22px;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .tl-content time {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-placeholder);
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .tl-content p {
    font-size: 0.93rem;
  }

  .tag-cloud {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .tag {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }

  .motto-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .motto-block blockquote {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-card);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-blue);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  }

  .motto-block blockquote p {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .connect-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .connect-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 16px 24px;
    color: inherit;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 180px;
  }

  .connect-card:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .connect-icon {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .connect-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
</style>
